{"tid":1052530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門醫院急症室醫生涉食大麻當值 醫管局徹查","createTime":"2019-03-08T10:56:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T17:12:55.000Z","uid":58851,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3640a5bbc25fffe897e6d26b0e67ee35cea95ff1","tid":1052530,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T10:56:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190308/59346380\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190308%2F59346380&d=fEJCtfATBeMWJ6YDVJZPMpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=6bd1ce00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190308%2F59346380&h=a68f8b5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190308/59346380</a><br />\n屯門醫院有醫生疑吸食大麻！《蘋果》獲悉，屯門醫院急症室一名副顧問醫生近日在當值期間疑突然「失蹤」，同事尋獲他時卻發現他神智迷糊。醫院同事擔心他身體有嚴重毛病，為他作身體檢查，包括尿液快速測試時，卻意發現其尿液疑含大麻。消息稱，醫管局高層對此事件感震驚，正進行詳細調查，涉事的副顧問醫生已被要求即時休假。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吸毒死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過勞死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />放假死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加假期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e4a5d5c4f5f8973432758b58decba0930b52b0","tid":1052530,"uid":7273,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T10:58:53.000Z","msg":"最衰都係編更果個，搞到追更要返工時隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e12e96793a5f5356c88dd378f4937fdb2822fed4","tid":1052530,"uid":58851,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3640a5bbc25fffe897e6d26b0e67ee3